						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Top of the stone door leading into the interior of the Raṅgamaṭha.</hi></p>						

						<p>17th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>The first ten lines of this inscription, in characters of the <hi rend="bold">17th Century A.D.,</hi> are engraved negatively. It seems to register a gift of some <hi rend="italic">Vṛittis</hi> to Siddhaswāmi of the <hi rend="italic">maṭha.</hi> </p>						

